channel.description: I need help with my server can someone please help or tell me step by step how to make one. i had one before but i took down. I portforwarded i have no-ip set up and all of that and i have a webclient on rswebclients it says its online but it don't allow me or anyone else to login can someone please tell me whats wrong? and I have my no-ip in my webclient and source and client files.

item.title: Trouble getting server online
item.dc:creator: @anthonyduka anthonyduka
item.description:
@anthonyduka wrote:

Okay, to get your server online follow these steps:

  1. open port 43954
  2. forward port 43594
  3. keep no-ip open
  4. run your server ( go to your server’s folder then press run)

if you dont know what i’m talking about by opening/forwarding the ports look it up on google.
